    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/b837807f7a0505370c30b9f374f31d25.poster.avif?t=1771493214\" aria-label=\"The timelapse of expanding realm by gradually building new settlements and recruiting new units.\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/b837807f7a0505370c30b9f374f31d25.webm?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/b837807f7a0505370c30b9f374f31d25.mp4?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">JOURNEY THROUGH THE AGES TO ASCEND YOUR EMPIRE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a nation from nothing into a thriving empire.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your economy, manage resources, and secure prosperity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raise a powerful army, expand your borders, and crush your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your realm to victory and carve your legacy into history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">MASTER WAR ACROSS ERAS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/01d90219a914b0ddb362ef80274b7777.poster.avif?t=1771493214\" aria-label=\"The scenario of a battle - moving units, attacking enemy troops emerging from the fog of war.\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/01d90219a914b0ddb362ef80274b7777.webm?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/01d90219a914b0ddb362ef80274b7777.mp4?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From tactical skirmishes to massive sieges, adapt your strategy to the evolving battlefield. A knight might dominate open plains, but crumble against fortified walls. Success requires a mix of unit types, calculated positioning and anticipation of your enemies’ next move. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight across procedurally generated maps, handcrafted battlefields, or fully custom scenarios - each shaped by rolling hills, natural choke points, vast oceans, dense forests, sandy shores and towering mountains. No two campaigns will ever play the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">ADVANCE THROUGH AGES</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/23153b4b033763d2bba94cc96cdd71db.poster.avif?t=1771493214\" aria-label=\"Overlook of technology tree available during the game.\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/23153b4b033763d2bba94cc96cdd71db.webm?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/23153b4b033763d2bba94cc96cdd71db.mp4?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin with humble villages and militias, then research technologies to unlock mighty siege engines, armored knights and more. As you progress, resources evolve, choices multiply and your world grows more complex - forcing sharper, more impactful strategic decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">A WORLD OF STRATEGY AWAITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.poster.avif?t=1771493214\" aria-label=\"Scenario from the game about the siege of a city done by a dragon, with units defending the settlement.\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.webm?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.mp4?t=1771493214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary battles, emergent narrative and endless exploration - build your own grandeur in an accessible entry to the turn-based strategy games. Do you have what it takes to ascend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
